s/^#INTRO/B<Clockwork> is a system configuration management system designed to securely\
enforce policies on one or more host systems.  It can ensure that files have the\
prescribed attributes (owner, group, permissions, etc.) and content.  It can maintain\
a specific set of installed packages, and even make sure that system user accounts exist./
s/^#SEEALSO/B<clockwork>(7), B<clockd>(1), B<clockd.conf>(5) and B<cogd.conf>(5)/
s/^#AUTHOR/Clockwork was designed and written by James Hunt./
